> **Info:** This class is located in `lot\extend\plugin\engine\kernel` folder.

### Version

~~~ .xmp.php
Plugin::version($id, $v = null);
~~~

Return the `version` property of `about.page` file in the current plugin folder or `0.0.0`:

~~~ .php
$test = Plugin::version('markdown');
~~~

### Info

~~~ .xmp.php
Plugin::info($id);
~~~

Return a page object of `about.page` file in the current plugin folder:

~~~ .php
$info = Plugin::info('markdown');
~~~

### Exist

~~~ .xmp.php
Plugin::exist($input, $fail = false);
~~~

Return the folder path of current plugin folder if exists:

~~~ .php
if ($path = Plugin::exist('markdown')) {
    // do something with `$path` â€¦
}
~~~

### State

~~~ .xmp.php
Plugin::state($id, $key = null, $fail = false);
~~~

Return the stored plugin states if any, otherwise, return `$fail`:

~~~ .php
$state = Plugin::state('markdown');
~~~

